data.description: Darling 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with granite counters in the kitchen along with 18 inch tiles on the  floor, New interior and exterior paint, new carpeting, new flooring in Laundry and new windows in patio/sun room.  In addition there are dual pane windows in most of the home, new mini blinds throughout, a nice sized yard and it is conveniently located less than a block from public transit.
